by the HMBT','History','','inherit','open','open','','141-revision-v1','','','2014-03-12 03:19:13','2014-03-12 03:19:13','',141,'http://handmaids-local/uncategorized/141-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(335,1,'2014-03-12 03:57:59','2014-03-12 03:57:59','[sidebar]Current Needs [subpages][/sidebar]\r\n\r\nThe HMBT order has relied entirely on receiving outside donations and generating of funds from within.  There is no steady stream of funding coming from any parent organization.   The HMBT is registered as an Indian NGO under the secular name Sneha Jewan Kendra which means Love and Life Center.  Effort is currently underway to register Sneha Jewan Kendra in the United States as a charitable 501 C 3 organization.\r\n\r\nOn this page you can see a list of the major current needs at the orphanages.  Your contribution is greatly appreciated.\r\n\r\n<form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\" target=\"_top\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"cmd\" value=\"_s-xclick\" />\r\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"hosted_button_id\" value=\"BGG3VL42SCA5L\" />\r\n<input type=\"image\" alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\" name=\"submit\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif\" />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /></form>','Give','','inherit','open','open','','11-revision-v1','','','2014-03-12 03:57:59','2014-03-12 03:57:59','',11,'http://handmaids-local/uncategorized/11-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(336,1,'2014-03-12 03:59:23','2014-03-12 03:59:23','[sidebar]<strong>Current Needs</strong> [subpages][/sidebar]\r\n\r\nThe HMBT order has relied entirely on receiving outside donations and generating of funds from within.  There is no steady stream of funding coming from any parent organization.   The HMBT is registered as an Indian NGO under the secular name Sneha Jewan Kendra which means Love and Life Center.  Effort is currently under